There is also a division between men and women.
While men "cool" the birch plant extract to make the mattress cover absorb heat and cool the body, women, on the contrary, "melt" the coatings.
Red pepper extract increases blood circulation, making the weaker sex warmer.
Today's favorites?
Mattress made of cold foam (has larger pores with broken cell structure, is more breathable than normal polyurethane and offers better elasticity.
The combination of different rigidities of cold foams and "lazy" foams creates multi-zone mattresses that know exactly where the head, thighs and heels should be.
For a quality mattress you will pay from seven thousand crowns and above.
Those who meet health parameters, have a lower VAT rate, are taken as medical aids.
Gumotex was the first to achieve this advantage in the Czech Republic.
Saving on a mattress and grill is not easy.
Sometimes you can take advantage of the actions of manufacturers or sellers who offer two mattresses for the price of one.
For example, the Magniflex brand offers a Duofreeze mattress with Memory foam in suture for 11,990 CZK.
The second one can already be purchased for free.
An era of lazy or viscoelastic foams with an open cellular structure and high density was initiated by the "cosmic" tempo of Tempur material.
It was originally created as a material for NASA because the astronauts were exposed to enormous congestion during the launches.
Tempur softens in the heat, in the cold it hardens.
It adapts perfectly to the warm human body and distributes its pressure optimally.
It is therefore ideal against the formation of bedspreads, but also for increased comfort during sleep.
Viscoelastic foams are used not only on mattresses, but also on medical products, for example, on special pillows under the feet, which relieve the feet and venous system.
Domestic manufacturers use, for example, Eucatherm C or Twinsaver foam and the like.
